title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, NFL on FOX’s Jay Glazer calls in for all the latest from around the NFL. MLB Network’s Jon Paul Morosi joins the guys to recap Game 5 of the World Series. Fox Sports 1 NBA Analyst Ric Bucher tells you if this is the end of the Warriors dynasty. And the guys give you their BIG bold predictions for Week 9 in the NFL!
